{"tid":126288,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐警盟　梁美芬：根據基本法　特首可特赦七警","createTime":"2017-02-19T08:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T06:26:21.000Z","uid":47714,"like":8,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"419a12af185f5fb6a7c4d662a014f6bd918cd77d","tid":126288,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:33:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/58a83f9a6db28c5423aa85cc/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F58a83f9a6db28c5423aa85cc%2F&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=88183119\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/58a83f9a6db28c5423aa85cc/</a><br />\n<br />\n「撐警大聯盟」等舉行記者會，指根據《基本法》第四十八條，行政長官有權赦免或減輕七名警員的刑罰，他們計劃星期日到禮賓府請願。<br />\n<br />\n本身是大律師的立法會議員，梁美芬認為可以考慮：「因為他們在執勤時，受到大環境的挑釁，是犯了事，在這個情況下的確行為是不對的，但是否有機會作為減刑。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=211190\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D211190&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=18756ce7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D211190&h=53852cc8\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=211190</a><br />\n<br />\n撐警大聯盟和警察員佐級協會創建人暨退役同僚聯會表示，對案件的裁決和判刑感到難過和痛心，要求行政長官行使基本法第48條賦予的權力，赦免七名警員的刑罰。<br />\n<br />\n大聯盟計劃在星期日下午到禮賓府向梁振英遞交請願信，下星期起亦會在全港各區設置街站收集市民簽名，支持七名警員。"},{"pid":"50dc5c6d4bba0ea38e3c7877b774dcb4410db5c1","tid":126288,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T08:35:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想屌問呢位影撚衰LSOB既盧犬：<br />\n<br />\n1. 出埋Judgement同Penalty而實際未有任何FormalAppeal，咁都唔係玩完法律程序？？你呢位執法CP厄飯食架？？<br />\n<br />\n2. 你同3萬隻義工黎架？？？你要睇3萬隻頭，就當幾百萬出你糧既透明呀？？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgm