赦權呢個漏洞。唔該土共唔好當香港人係唔識法律，《基本法》係法律，唔係俾你班友亂咁解釋。<br />\n<br />\n點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佔中完全侵犯其他公民的權利，已被習近平及689，定性左。</span>7警因為平定違法佔中，而行駛左不符合法律的武力，但本質上係維護返其他公民的權利。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港行英式法律<br />\n唔係領導人定性左就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a989031d63788409898b0a994937d4982b50f69a","tid":126288,"uid":12370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T10:45:07.000Z","msg":"其實唔係話夠唔夠膽，而係特赦完隨時引發第二次佔中或者旺角衝突，689先唔會係自己任期完前搞單野來燒埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b449e279e56547587c6c24b9268b18913896bca","tid":126288,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:02:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實唔係話夠唔夠膽，而係特赦完隨時引發第二次佔中或者旺角衝突，689先唔會係自己任期完前搞單野來燒埋自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nDQ兩位民選議員都無 第二次雨革<br />\n<br />\n反而特赦會有??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a0135d15ffba5523641cd067526a7d48181bf6","tid":126288,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T11:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今次我撐佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夠薑咪試下</blockquote><br />\n一特赦又準備開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f173051f9402f637300fae66700889d8c6b5fa","tid":126288,"uid":24257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":